7️⃣ Security Architecture Summary

Redemption allowed only if:

✔ Valid JWT
✔ Within 200m
✔ Timestamp < 60s
✔ Device ID present
✔ Not replayed
✔ Not fraud-flagged

This satisfies the PRD security section and closes GPS spoof gap.
